      "narrative": {
        "News": "Marathon - Mandan: the 74,000 bpd CDU and 27,000 bpd FCC were restarted during the morning of July 1. Also, increased activi- ty began at the 23,800 bpd diesel hydrotreater, 4,300 bpd gasoline hydrotreater and 4,400 bpd alkylation unit during the morning of July 1. All monitored units were shut during the evening of June 29.",
